{"tid":1190301,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一早決定左9號要出去，但條女買左船飛去澳門。。。","createTime":"2019-06-07T08:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T17:53:20.000Z","uid":18552,"like":553,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"fedaa43e2d5059a58f0674978fb9bb851270251b","tid":1190301,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"之前一早就同佢講左，<br />\n但係早排突然有日佢同我講話買左飛去澳門，<br />\n我又醒唔起個係香港人最要嘅日子，<br />\n不過依家我決定唔同佢去澳門，<br />\n所以佢嬲撚左我，<br />\n同佢講左香港發生緊咩事，<br />\n佢都係要企係高地話做咩都改變唔到，<br />\n話今次當你地成功，<br />\n下之中國又會玩野改少少野又再推多次，<br />\n所以點都係無用 香港玩完咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話咩我唔去就搵其他人陪佢去，<br />\n問佢同邊個佢又話唔講我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔支持唔緊要，<br />\n但唔係同我係咁放負，<br />\n係咁同我講失敗論咖。<br />\n自從雨革之後，香港好多人都好負，<br />\n點解咁難得大家可以有共同目標可以行番出黎都要咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國難當前我真係無心機去玩，對唔住<br />\n<br />\n希望 9號大家可以一齊出黎 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3798955959aebe8311777d6284a6b30c6521d80","tid":1190301,"uid":142358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c8ac4406b612c3d267790007722099a5011bba","tid":1190301,"uid":18552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3798955959aebe8311777d6284a6b30c6521d80","tid":1190301,"uid":142358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"大家要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5affb9b9722c58d8d94fafc2cb42751fcafce22f","tid":1190301,"uid":1696,"like":201,"dislike":9,"score":192,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"巴打好波<br />\n<br />\n得罪都要講句<br />\n呢d 女真係要唔過<br />\